      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior presents beautifully in its original factory paint, showing only minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the front fascia and a small, shallow scuff on the lower rear bumper. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin has been kept in impressive shape; the leather seats remain soft and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and sunroof, operate exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, backed by a comprehensive service history that includes recent fluid flushes and a new battery. The transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. This car has been a non-smoker vehicle and has been garage-kept, ensuring it remains a dependable and sharp-looking choice for its next owner.",
